title: Need players for ranked 5s team
body:
Hey there guys,
I've recently started a ranked 5s team on OCE, and wanted people who take ranked seriously and do not troll. My team is currently looking for a top lane, and AD Carry.
If you have any messages or would like to join please feel free to message me in game, and i'll list my name below.
IGN: Sharko
Thank you for taking the time to read
